metadata.name: Loulan - The Dune Duchess
metadata.description:
The derivatives art inspired by Lives of Asuna 5168

"...大田三年，積粟百萬，威服外國..." 
This man stutters and mumbles his words

"Come, outsider, welcome to my reign"

As the dune duchess invites you to visit her reign, she carefully hides her wings in case she scares anyone
